Dale Hollow Lake State Resort Park |publisher=Kentucky Department of Parks |accessdate=September 26, 2013}}</ref> The park comprises {{convert|3400|acre}}.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://parks.ky.gov/burkesville/parks/resort/dale-hollow-lake-state-resort-park Dale Hollow Lake State Resort Park] Kentucky Department of Parks\n*[http://www.lrn.usace.army.mil/Locations/Lakes/DaleHollowLake.aspx Dale Hollow Lake] U.S. Army Corps of Engineers Nashville District\n\n{{Kentucky Parks}}\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:State parks of Kentucky]]\n[[Category:Protected areas of Cumberland County, Kentucky]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox protected area\n| name            = Dale Hollow Lake State Resort Park\n| iucn_category   = \n| iucn_ref        = \n<!-- images -->\n| photo           = \n| photo_caption   = \n<!-- map -->\n| map             = USA Kentucky\n| map_image       = \n| map_size        = \n| map_caption     = Location in Kentucky\n| relief          = \n<!-- location -->\n| location        = [[Clinton County, Kentucky|Clinton]], [[Cumberland County, Kentucky|Cumberland]], Kentucky, United States\n| nearest_city    = \n| nearest_town    = \n| coordinates     = {{coord|36|38|19|N|85|17|53|W|display=inline,title}}\n| coords_ref      = \n<!-- stats --> \n| length          = \n| length_mi       = \n| length_km       = \n| width           = \n| width_mi        = \n| width_km        = \n| area_acre       = 3400\n| area_ref        = \n| elevation       = {{convert|1040|ft|m|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite gnis|2567979|Dale Hollow Lake State Park}}</ref>\n| elevation_avg   = \n| elevation_min   = \n| elevation_max   = \n| dimensions      = \n| designation     = \n<!-- dates & info -->\n| authorized      = \n| created         = \n| designated      = \n| established     = 1978<ref name=history/>\n| named_for       = \n| visitation_num  = \n| visitation_year = \n| visitation_ref  = \n| governing_body  = Kentucky Department of Parks\n| administrator   = \n|